"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Are you all in or crypto? Investing 100% of crypto. \\n\\nI strongly believe that everyone should invest in crypto, but I am concerned about those who have invested a high percentage of their savings into crypto. These people might be the Maximalists or new people in crypto, who might have recently gotten in the crypto world seeing others make extra ordinary gains. Please understand that crypto is a long-term game. There can be another crypto winter, in which coins may loose their value by 90% or more. No body can really predict when the next crypto winter will come. Therefore if one invests in crypto they should always be ready for a 90% or more crash and have some alternative back up to have some earnings. Everyone has a different risk profile, but I think everyone should invest at least 20% of their savings in crypto. Even if you loose 20% of your savings, it is not a deal breaker.\",\"timestamp\":1642230772,\"title\":\"All In or Not\"},\"digest\":\"pk47K3rb2mij-vTOyhIAneTUnuF-HyiPkerCFY24R_E\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE3bbbA53569069C00f9b743b9dD1B1B9658F21eb\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ThPsGK0iP_T5fOFY7GVtl3bb5-PrjzRDmuFCiawxRfA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hRNhBIGkf8cU2A0ZbS23510kp3iL5WpSHPnB7Nyav8k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"HOeHFJsi6o52ATjbY1W02SzjkbGCwuL9K_BSmj010XxP68n33nZqr1jDOECGXD0JgQCovk-o6nm52Pl9x1t_pw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6d86834eb6247d19379695aef5e03be8e1af4b745b2fb154475dc16920f7e4c3588cdbcfbdd9ffa7a6842767ecd57f1b729c3bd4d3ffe5fdd2ef76500a8fd5b11c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ThPsGK0iP_T5fOFY7GVtl3bb5-PrjzRDmuFCiawxRfA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hRNhBIGkf8cU2A0ZbS23510kp3iL5WpSHPnB7Nyav8k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\